486
00:34:59,890 --> 00:35:02,650
Aku menunggu hari
di mana kau dipermalukan.

487
00:35:06,220 --> 00:35:07,460
Menambah ujian fisik?

488
00:35:09,740 --> 00:35:12,760
Maharani tentu tahu
bahwa Qu Tan'er sangat lemah.

489
00:35:13,090 --> 00:35:14,980
Namun, sengaja memberinya
ujian fisik?

490
00:35:15,330 --> 00:35:17,130
